Shadow Hand (Stance)
Level: Swordsage 3, Saint 3
Initiation Action: 1 swift action
Range: Personal
Target: You
Duration: Stance

While you are in this stance, your skill in Move Silently becomes equal to your skill in Hide.  This bonus includes all feat, item, and effect bonuses.  This ability has no effect if your skill in Move Silently is equal to or greater than your skill in Hide.

This maneuver is a supernatural ability.